<DOC><DOCNO> DOE2-06-0474 </DOCNO><TEXT>Calculations on the ECR absorption of electromagnetic waves in the plasmaof the L-2 stellarator are reported. A numerical simulation yields resultswhich explain the qualitative features of experiments carried out inthe L-2 stellarator in terms of the single-pass absorption of a quasiopticalbeam of extraordinary waves.</TEXT></DOC>